Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.83,0:01:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.78,0:01:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you do, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.33,0:01:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too good, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.88,0:01:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get enough sleep, so I couldn't think.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.93,0:01:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot, that's what you get for studying all night.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.05,0:01:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I actually spent the whole night giving demons back their names.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.18,0:01:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I can't tell him that, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.51,0:02:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the test's over!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.02,0:02:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere to celebrate.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.10,0:02:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys going somewhere again?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.11,0:02:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Leave us alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.89,0:02:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.71,0:02:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, I want to go to this art museum!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.11,0:02:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.34,0:02:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go fishing again?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.96,0:02:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to mix it up a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.78,0:02:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's autumn, want to go grape picking?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.38,0:02:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.59,0:02:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to go somewhere that will give us lasting life lessons.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.96,0:02:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my idea of a good time.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey guys, let's go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.02,0:02:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.43,0:02:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.86,0:02:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to go have fun somewhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.97,0:02:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the beach.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.21,0:02:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too cold for the beach.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.57,0:02:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking that you've changed lately, Tanuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.62,0:03:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We were in different classes, so I didn't really know,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.29,0:03:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but I never thought of you as the talkative type.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.77,0:03:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd be talking about stupid stuff with those guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.53,0:03:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying we always talk about stupid stuff?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.46,0:03:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, he's just like us.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.47,0:03:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.01,0:03:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And that goes for Tanuma, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.54,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you were transfer students,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and you didn't talk very much when you first got here.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.35,0:03:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.72,0:03:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you guys would be cooler.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.98,0:03:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you turned out to be just like us.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.16,0:03:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the two of you both seem to collapse from anemia all the time.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's, uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.66,0:03:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.49,0:03:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.05,0:03:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are we going fishing again?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.04,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who said we needed to mix it up a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.45,0:03:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this means we're all grown up.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When little kids go out to play,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.86,0:04:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,they can have all kinds of fun in an empty lot.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.16,0:04:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so that's what you mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.82,0:04:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As people grow older, they learn to put aside childish things.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.65,0:04:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, we'll be learning how adults have fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.17,0:04:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How adults have fun?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.25,0:04:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.45,0:04:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, when you were a kid, anything you did was fun,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.61,0:04:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,so it wasn't so hard to find something to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.33,0:04:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.73,0:04:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We did something different every day.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.21,0:04:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do when you were kids?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.21,0:04:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I played house, tiddlywinks...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.01,0:04:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to go exploring!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.32,0:04:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Exploring?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.52,0:04:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.52,0:04:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd take some kids from the neighborhood and go out to the reservoir.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.35,0:04:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents got really mad at me for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.13,0:04:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to do things like that, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.49,0:04:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I played hide and seek on the temple grounds,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.89,0:04:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and one time I hid in this really important shrine building,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and when my dad found me, he whipped me good.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.37,0:05:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody played tag and hide-and-seek.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.11,0:05:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow tag!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.08,0:05:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to play shadow tag all the time.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.38,0:05:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If somebody stepped on your shadow, you were "it".
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.65,0:05:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that one.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody does.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.34,0:05:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.69,0:05:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I watched the other kids play, but I never joined them.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.23,0:05:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We never decided on where to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.14,0:05:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You shot down everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.28,0:05:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where do you want to go, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.43,0:05:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.57,0:05:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,anywhere would be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.02,0:05:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can all go together, any place would be fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.71,0:05:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.83,0:05:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Say cheese!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.25,0:06:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.83,0:06:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher gave me this for the cultural fair.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked me to take some pictures for the senior yearbook.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.89,0:06:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior yearbook?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a little early for that?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.21,0:06:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.78,0:06:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be long at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.35,0:06:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanuma, are you going to take over the temple after you graduate?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.58,0:06:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't really thought about it yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.78,0:06:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be nice to be a priest.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno what I'll do.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.01,0:06:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you need to start thinking about college and work.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My future, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.95,0:06:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to think about it, for Touko and Shigeru.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.40,0:06:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what kind of work can I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.38,0:06:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's enjoy being high schoolers a little longer before we decide.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.98,0:06:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that sounds good.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.32,0:07:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Takashi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.41,0:07:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How was your test?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.65,0:07:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It went okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.60,0:07:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.28,0:07:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.90,0:07:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.65,0:07:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making tempura today.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Change and come downstairs.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.71,0:07:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.46,0:07:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it a taste.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.29,0:07:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.94,0:07:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.20,0:07:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.77,0:07:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it needs some sauce.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shigeru!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.38,0:07:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't eat until dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.86,0:07:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi can do it, but I can't?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.81,0:07:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a shrimp!\N Those are for everybody to share!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, come on. I'm just eating one.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.93,0:07:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. You get one less.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.73,0:07:47.72,Default - Overlap,,0,0,0,,I'll go get changed.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.41,0:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Mister Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.96,0:07:55.41,Default - Overlap,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.41,0:07:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's everybody doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Master call you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.17,0:08:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I call them?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.34,0:08:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They have something to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you guys want?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No trouble this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.68,0:08:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.76,0:08:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to tell you that tomorrow is the Spirit Moon.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.77,0:08:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sake tastes especially good that night.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum, yum.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.46,0:08:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Spirit Moon?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.93,0:08:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.49,0:08:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, the position of the stars is especially good this year,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.30,0:08:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,making the sake several times better than usual.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.63,0:08:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're all getting together tomorrow afternoon for a drinking party.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.31,0:08:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Drinking party!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, all the spirits who know you
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.20,0:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,have gotten together to throw the first annual
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.08,0:08:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Party for Mister Natsume in the Run-down Old Shrine Near Yatsuhara"!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.74,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Run-down, run-down.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.13,0:08:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A party for those who have to put up with Mister Natsume's whining and meddling,{*}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.33,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and run to him like a dog if he needs us.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.18,0:09:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You could call us the "Natsume Dogs"!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.19,0:09:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Bark!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of name is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.40,0:09:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll be coming to pick you up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.53,0:09:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to let you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm not going.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.88,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds shady.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a spoilsport.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.57,0:09:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you can hang out with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang out, hang out!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.29,0:09:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please join us, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, you guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.40,0:09:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi, come down.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.53,0:09:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, just go home for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.55,0:09:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.14,0:09:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Nyanko, you're my bodyguard, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.17,0:09:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something about them.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.57,0:09:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? You should go.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.27,0:09:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be more fun than you think.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.07,0:09:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You just want to drink.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.92,0:09:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.75,0:09:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.82,0:10:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitty!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.76,0:10:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitty!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.78,0:10:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume, do something!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Taki?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't get cursed again, did you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.52,0:10:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I decided something.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.84,0:10:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to understand the research my grandfather did on demons.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.29,0:10:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I won't mess around with anything dangerous.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.28,0:10:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When I draw my circles, I don't complete them,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and I always erase them.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.65,0:10:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But sometimes I like to practice, like you just saw.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.69,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It might help you out someday.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry about me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.90,0:11:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want everything my grandfather worked for to disappear.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.11,0:11:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.57,0:11:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I'm going to do with myself after high school,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.88,0:11:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but for now, I can do this much, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.97,0:11:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.75,0:11:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please return my name.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.33,0:11:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.42,0:11:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.98,0:11:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's help him out.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.48,0:11:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.28,0:11:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta do something.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.75,0:11:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on without me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.53,0:11:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.32,0:11:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That which shields me, reveal thy name.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I return your name.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.33,0:12:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.39,0:12:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the demon from this morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.09,0:12:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He fell for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.79,0:12:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo! Yahoo! Yahoo! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.67,0:12:56.99,Default - Overlap,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.79,0:13:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!{ends on scenechange}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.64,0:13:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.39,0:13:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Natsume. You're late.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.73,0:13:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.90,0:13:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite late. And you smell as you always do.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.71,0:13:19.46,Default - Overlap,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.63,0:13:22.34,Default - Overlap,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.34,0:13:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come sit by me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.91,0:13:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.62,0:13:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to drink three for being late.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.14,0:13:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm a minor.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.40,0:13:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always so stiff.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.83,0:13:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That tickles.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.88,0:13:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.21,0:13:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.88,0:13:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I came for the free drinks. So all this is for you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Benio.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mister Madara.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.59,0:13:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still in that pitiful, tiny form.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.81,0:13:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just shallow.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.56,0:13:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know someone who adores this form!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Although she's a human girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.36,0:13:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.80,0:14:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You know a lot of powerful demons, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.25,0:14:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You dance too!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.37,0:14:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.01,0:14:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Natsume, what do humans do for fun when they gather like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.97,0:14:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.05,0:14:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they do for fun?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.42,0:14:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They play cards...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and when they're outside,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.26,0:14:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe kick the can or shadow tag.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow tag? That sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.61,0:14:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If Mister Natsume can't drink,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,then let's play that shadow tag game with him!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.61,0:14:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.99,0:14:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, I didn't―
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.84,0:14:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume, how do you play that game?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.62,0:14:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know tag, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.49,0:14:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like that, but if the one who's "it" steps on your shadow, then you're "it".{*}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.63,0:15:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"It", huh?  Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.61,0:15:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, if you catch somebody, you get to eat them, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.21,0:15:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you definitely can't.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.84,0:15:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the point is to run from the person who's "it",
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.39,0:15:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and hide from them so they can't step on your shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.54,0:15:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then shouldn't you just hide in a shadow?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.06,0:15:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, you can't do that for more than five seconds.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.54,0:15:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be "it" first.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You can run anywhere on the shrine grounds.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.65,0:15:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.45,0:15:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They all ran off.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.87,0:15:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stay away!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.37,0:15:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't come over here!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Liar Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get lost!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.40,0:15:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get lost!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.22,0:15:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a drink.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.46,0:15:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here! He's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.22,0:15:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you, Moustache!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.49,0:16:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, how foolish of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.61,0:16:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a creature with short legs.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.75,0:16:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I stepped on your shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.00,0:16:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're "it"!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.28,0:16:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda pissed now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.22,0:16:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My beastly blood roars!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.81,0:16:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.94,0:16:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,stepped...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...on your shadow!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.49,0:16:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume, prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.52,0:16:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.49,0:16:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not "it" anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No complaining!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.13,0:17:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop running, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.04,0:17:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.17,0:17:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't joke with me, Master Nyanko.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.08,0:17:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be my bodyguard.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think you can get away with this!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.23,0:17:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him, Mister Madara!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.69,0:17:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No mercy for humans!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.44,0:17:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.68,0:17:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that anything but stepping on somebody's shadow
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,was against the rules!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.28,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That was dangerous.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.27,0:17:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing that was against the rules, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.12,0:17:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I was the first one Mister Madara stepped on,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.61,0:17:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,let's get back to work!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.59,0:17:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.95,0:17:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Lord Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.88,0:17:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You've guts to call us "dogs".
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.74,0:17:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Cyclops's idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.81,0:17:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I stepped on your shadow!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.72,0:18:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're "it", Mister Misuzu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.48,0:18:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so I'm "it"?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.48,0:18:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.47,0:18:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.53,0:18:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to step on the shadow of the players who run.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.07,0:18:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.56,0:18:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like a fun game.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.18,0:18:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, run, lesser beings.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.12,0:18:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu, sorry, but could you be the referee?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.34,0:18:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,One... two... three...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.34,0:18:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you step on somebody's shadow, you can\N do whatever you want with them, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.84,0:18:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no rule like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.10,0:18:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it!  You should run with your shadow in front of you!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.31,0:18:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Run to the north!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.16,0:18:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.69,0:18:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this game?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.09,0:18:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's endless.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.76,0:18:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are terrifying creatures to think of such a game.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.62,0:19:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume, how does this end?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.94,0:19:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've never actually played it,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.38,0:19:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.54,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've never played it before?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.63,0:19:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.97,0:19:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can see how much fun it was for everyone I watched when I was little.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.66,0:19:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.17,0:19:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know when I started meeting so many spirits.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.72,0:19:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if Reiko was ever able to feel like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.66,0:19:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're "it" next, Mister Madara?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's make this our last game.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.94,0:19:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If he steps on your shadow, you're out.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.16,0:19:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he steps on them all, he wins.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.66,0:19:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.06,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That means the one who's "it" has to do a lot of work!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.04,0:19:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,An excellent idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.04,0:19:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone whose shadow is stepped on has to go inside this circle.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go in that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.43,0:19:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.55,0:20:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Begin!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.41,0:20:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.10,0:20:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you all!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.92,0:20:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's one!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.93,0:20:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dead!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, one more.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.29,0:20:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.49,0:20:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I fell down a hole?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.59,0:20:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess nobody will step on my shadow if I'm down here.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.27,0:20:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.41,0:20:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me catch you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.16,0:20:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's dumb enough to wait  just because you tell them to.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.38,0:20:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.17,0:20:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.88,0:20:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is your name Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.02,0:20:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wanna play?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every time I moved,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.23,0:20:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}plenty of kids would talk to me at first.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.05,0:20:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, I'd say things they didn't understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.41,0:20:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course they didn't like people they thought were liars.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.83,0:20:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Liar Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.23,0:20:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stay away, Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.40,0:20:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.90,0:21:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}New kid! Come with us!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.70,0:21:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're lucky you get to move a lot.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.91,0:21:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You must go lots of places and see lots of people.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.57,0:21:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.51,0:21:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.52,0:21:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}See you!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.28,0:21:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.68,0:21:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Nyanko!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.01,0:21:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the clumsiest kid I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.89,0:21:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.46,0:21:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the last one.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.49,0:21:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you step on my shadow, it's over?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.90,0:21:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So what, are you gonna stay down there forever?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.40,0:21:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't get up.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull me up!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.72,0:21:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.62,0:21:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a pain, you know that?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.96,0:21:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.66,0:22:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.88,0:22:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.42,0:22:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He got you, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are weak.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.72,0:22:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.46,0:22:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He got you all, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.31,0:22:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Madara wins!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.22,0:22:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's drink to celebrate!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.17,0:22:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Celebrate! Celebrate!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.73,0:22:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being weak.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.69,0:22:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll protect you.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.95,0:22:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone weak like you called us, we wouldn't have a choice.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.16,0:22:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We like you, so we'd have to protect you!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.78,0:22:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.95,0:22:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.38,0:22:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going over to Tanuma's.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.89,0:22:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish planning our trip.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.64,0:22:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:59.91,0:23:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:01.85,0:23:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something there?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:04.33,0:23:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.60,0:23:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:09.26,0:23:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to play with them a bit more.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.35,0:23:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.24,0:23:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.37,0:23:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.18,0:23:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.93,0:23:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes, I've hated being able to see demons.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.93,0:23:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.58,0:23:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}seeing them has also let me meet so many different people.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:38.64,0:23:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I can feel grateful.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.05,0:23:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:49.23,0:23:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, both humans and demons
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.23,0:23:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are equally irreplacable to me.
